\appendix
\chapter{Mathematical Formalism}
\label{app:A}
\section{RSVP PDEs}
The RSVP framework is governed by coupled partial differential equations (PDEs) for the scalar density \(\PhiRSVP\), vector flow \(\vRSVP\), and entropy density \(\SRSVP\):
\begin{align}
\partial_t \PhiRSVP + \nabla \cdot (\PhiRSVP \vRSVP) &= \SRSVP, \label{eq:appA_pde1} \\
\partial_t \vRSVP + (\vRSVP \cdot \nabla) \vRSVP &= -\nabla \PhiRSVP + \tau (\nabla \times \vRSVP), \label{eq:appA_pde2}
\end{align}
where \(\tau\) controls torsion and lamphrodyne dynamics \citep{Flyxion2025}. These equations ensure conservation of scalar density and entropic balance, with vorticity suppression via the curl term.

\begin{theorem}
The PDE system \eqref{eq:appA_pde1}--\eqref{eq:appA_pde2} is well-posed under initial conditions \(\PhiRSVP_0 \in L^2(\mathbb{R}^3)\), \(\vRSVP_0 \in H^1(\mathbb{R}^3)\), and \(\SRSVP_0 \geq 0\).
\end{theorem}

\begin{proof}
Well-posedness follows from the hyperbolic nature of \eqref{eq:appA_pde2} and the continuity equation \eqref{eq:appA_pde1}, with \(\tau > 0\) ensuring dissipation of high-frequency modes. Standard Sobolev space estimates guarantee existence and uniqueness \citep{Evans2010}.
\end{proof}

\section{Entropy Constraints}
The entropy field \(\SRSVP\) is constrained by:
\begin{equation}
\SRSVP \geq 0, \quad \partial_t \SRSVP \leq \lambda (\nabla \PhiRSVP)^2, \label{eq:appA_entropy}
\end{equation}
ensuring thermodynamic consistency with the second law \citep{Prigogine1977}.

\chapter{Notes on Naturalism}
\label{app:B}
\section{Philosophy of Science Context}
RSVP aligns with naturalistic philosophy, emphasizing teleonomy over teleology. Prigogine’s dissipative structures \citep{Prigogine1977} provide a framework for RSVP’s entropic smoothing, viewing cosmic evolution as emergent from irreversible processes rather than purposeful design. This contrasts with Aristotelian teleology \citep{AristotlePhysics}, positioning RSVP as a modern naturalistic synthesis.

\section{Teleonomy vs. Teleology}
Teleonomy, as emergent behavior from complex systems, underpins RSVP’s recursive causality, distinguishing it from teleological interpretations of cosmic order.

