Cauchy’s work on PDEs \citep{Cauchy1821} underpins RSVP’s governing equations \eqref{eq:pde1}--\eqref{eq:pde2}, ensuring rigorous convergence and stability.

\section{Stress Tensor}
The RSVP stress tensor is derived from \eqref{eq:action}, aligning with Cauchy’s formalism.

